$$
\rho = \left[ \begin{array}{c c c c} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 \\ 2 & 3 & 4 & 1 \end{array} \right],
$$

whereas a reflection across a horizontal axis yields

$$
\phi = \left[ \begin{array}{c c c c} 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 \\ 2 & 1 & 4 & 3 \end{array} \right].
