$$
D _ {6} = \left\{R _ {0}, R _ {1 2 0}, R _ {2 4 0}, F, R _ {1 2 0} F, R _ {2 4 0} F \right\} \times \left\{R _ {0}, R _ {1 8 0} \right\}.
