(a b H) ^ {i} = (a b) ^ {i} H = (a H) ^ {- 1} = a ^ {- 1} H = a H.
$$

It follows that

$$
\langle a H, b H \rangle = \langle a H, a b H \rangle \subseteq \langle a b H \rangle .
